            h1 Hire Me
            p Enqure about hiring me
      section
         .container
            .row
               .col-sm-10.col-md-8.col-lg-6.col-sm-offset-1.col-md-offset-2.col-lg-offset-3
                  .hireme-inner
                     .row
                        p.
                           Plesse fill out the form below to enquire about hiring me. To learn about how I work and the value I can bring to your project, please visit <a href='../about.html'>About</a> or to see what I'vs produced for other clients, view my <a href='#'>Protfolio</a>.
